    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">            </span>You imbue the chosen spectral arm with additional power that stems from your source of strength. Your next three Strikes with the imbued weapon deal an additional 2d6 spirit damage on a hit, or half on a miss as spectral blades or chains join your attack. Once it has been used to Strike thrice or when its duration expires, the spectral arm shatters.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><u>Special</u>: When you use a Mourneblade for Distortion Blade, or an Ethereal Chain for Smiting Chain while the weapon is under the effects of Shadowbreaker, you can add the bonus damage to each target hit by your spell; after completing the spell, the spectral arm shatters.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Heightened</strong>(+2): The additional damage increases by 1d6.</p>"
